<section autotoc="On this page"><title>SECTION 3: KNOW THYSELF</title>
    <section id="overview"><title>Overview</title>
        <p><img alt="[Window on the world]" src="./main.png"/>
        </p>
        <p>The main part of the screen shows you (center) and a small area of the Daimonin world in all its isometric glory.
        </p>
        <p>Surrounding this are all manner of displays, statistics, and icons. For the most part these record information about you and your current circumstances.
        </p>
        <p>The tables and displays across the top of the screen contain information about your identity, abilities, and current state of health. This section details that information.
        </p>
    </section>
